Working Together - Rock Hill Capital





















Investor Login
Click to be redirected to a secure third party site.



Phone 713.715.7510
Email



At Rock Hill we see ourselves as partners to our portfolio companies and trusted stewards to our investors.


We guide companies to greater growth by collaborating with owners to look for operational efficiencies, growth opportunities, greater revenue and margin improvements. But before we commit, our rigorous due diligence process provides us with a thorough understanding of the business and how to add value and growth. During due diligence, we evaluate a company's management organization, market opportunity, competitive advantages, financial performance and future capital needs. This critical process allows Rock Hill to gather key information, enabling us to discover the most effective ways to enhance performance and increase value.
This fact-finding allows us to invest with confidence and commitment, while providing our investors and entrepreneurial partners the assurance that we understand the business. 
Ultimately, Rock Hill helps transform entrepreneurial businesses into companies that reach their full potential and maximize value over time.
Learn more about investing with us and growing your company.








About Rock Hill Capital - Private Equity Fund - Texas





















Investor Login
Click to be redirected to a secure third party site.



Phone 713.715.7510
Email



Founded in 2007, Rock Hill Capital is a private equity firm based in Houston, Texas.


We are a private equity firm that invests in small–to lower middle market companies located in the South and Southeast U.S. with an enterprise value of up to $60 million. We focus on industrial products and services businesses.
We collaborate with experienced entrepreneurs in search of capital and the operational expertise they need to continue growing and expanding their business. We commit fearlessly to building successful companies over time to maximize value for both our portfolio businesses and our investors.
We have the confidence to follow through on our investments based on years of hands-on business experience and know-how. Governed by several principles that inform our actions and help us lend our expertise in the ideal manner, we work side-by-side with our entrepreneurial partners to help grow a company to its full market potential.
Learn more about the principles by which we lead, our history and our investment team.





