Rock Hill Capital Group, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:20 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Rock Hill Capital Group, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Rock Hill Capital Group, LLC is a private equity firm specializing in investments in recapitalizations, management buyouts, growth initiatives, financial restructuring, private family owned companies, troubled companies that are in need of capital, restructuring, or other financial re-engineering. The firm does not consider investments in operational or management turnarounds. It seeks to invest in small, growing small to lower middle market companies. It seeks to invest in industrial products and services, energy services, business services, and value-added distribution sectors. It prefers to invest in the companies based in Gulf Coast and Southern United States including the Southeast regi...
Rock Hill Capital Group, LLC is a private equity firm specializing in investments in recapitalizations, management buyouts, growth initiatives, financial restructuring, private family owned companies, troubled companies that are in need of capital, restructuring, or other financial re-engineering. The firm does not consider investments in operational or management turnarounds. It seeks to invest in small, growing small to lower middle market companies. It seeks to invest in industrial products and services, energy services, business services, and value-added distribution sectors. It prefers to invest in the companies based in Gulf Coast and Southern United States including the Southeast regions. The firm seeks to invest in companies with an enterprise value of less than $75 million and having EBITDA between $2 million and $10 million. It makes majority and control investments. Rock Hill Capital Group, LLC was founded in 2007 and is based in Houston, Texas.
